basic.description: Examination of the evolution of the traditional French-Canadian literature, especially the novel. Travaux pratiques include tests, an oral presentation and an in-depth essay. Given jointly with FREN 334/3.0.
basic.subject: FREN
basic.title: La littérature canadienne-française des débuts à 1965

extra.enrollment_requirement:
Prerequisites     FREN212 and FREN220 and Level 4 and registration in a FREN or FRLG Plan.
Exclusion     No more than 3.0 units from FREN334 ; FREN434; FREN402
